\left| {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}    2 & 6 & 4 & 0  \\    2 & 0 & 4 & 2  \\    0 & 3 & 2 & 1  \\    2 & 6 & 4 & 8  \\ \end{array}} \right| = \left| {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}    2 & 6 & 4 & 0  \\    0 & { - 6} & 0 & 2  \\    0 & 3 & 2 & 1  \\    0 & 0 & 0 & 8  \\ \end{array}} \right| = 2\left| {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}    { - 6} & 0 & 2  \\    3 & 2 & 1  \\    0 & 0 & 8  \\ \end{array}} \right| = 2*8\left| {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}    { - 6} & 0  \\    3 & 2  \\ \end{array}} \right| = 16*( - 12 - 0) =  - 192
-192
